            "title": "【異動股】京基金融數字科技等急瀉 被深交所調出港股通名單",
            "description": "<p>深交所公布，調整港股通標的證券名單，自今日起生效，當中多隻獲調出的股份急瀉。</p>\n<p>被調出名單的創夢天地(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01119' >01119</a>)大跌10.9%；京基金融(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01468' >01468</a>)狂瀉29.3%；數字科技(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01942' >01942</a>)急跌27.2%；創新奇智(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02121' >02121</a>)重創23.7%；海倫司(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/09869' >09869</a>)急挫19.2%；星空華文(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/06698' >06698</a>)急跌28.3%；永達(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/03669' >03669</a>)瀉7.3%；新特(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01799' >01799</a>)急跌7.2%；來凱(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02105' >02105</a>)大跌15.2%；奈雪的茶(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02150' >02150</a>)急跌18.9%。</p>\n<p>至於獲調入的晶苑(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02232' >02232</a>)，股價目前爆升一成二；訊飛醫療(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02506' >02506</a>)則大升11.1%；中旅(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00308' >00308</a>)爆升9.4%；衛龍美味(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/09985' >09985</a>)大升9.8%；方舟健客(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/06086' >06086</a>)勁升45%；鷹君(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00041' >00041</a>)則升3%；毛戈平(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01318' >01318</a>)大升9.6%；首程(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00697' >00697</a>)飆5.1%。</p>\n<p>立即試用<a href=\"https://www.ejfq.com/home.htm?source=sapo9\" target=\"_blank\">EJFQ「信號」全方位股票分析系統</a>，運用100+選股條件篩選值博股！</p>   </div>\n        ",
